### Get a single user (REST happy path)
GET http://localhost:8080/users/1
Accept: application/json

### List all users (REST collection)
GET http://localhost:8080/users
Accept: application/json

### Missing user (REST 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/users/999
Accept: application/json

### Streaming AI recommendation (SSE)
GET http://localhost:8080/recommendations?for=headphones
Accept: text/event-stream
